'From Squeak3.7beta of ''1 April 2004'' [latest update: #5948] on 10 June 2004 at 7:43:46 am'!"Change Set:		MCZInstallerFileListFix-nkDate:			8 June 2004Author:			Ned KonzFixes a problem in the MczInstaller in the image where the MczInstaller will offer its services for every file, not just .mcz files.This presents a confusing and broken 'Load' button on every file."!!MczInstaller class methodsFor: 'services' stamp: 'nk 6/8/2004 17:29'!fileReaderServicesForFile: fileName suffix: suffix	^({ self extension. '*' } includes: suffix)		ifTrue: [ self services ]		ifFalse: [#()].! !